chatg / chatgroup             Sends a message to a group of chat contacts

   Format:
      ;chatg <group> <text>   Sends the <text> to the <group>

   Notes:
      The Chat task is used to chat with other players directly via telnet.
         Calls can be placed (or accepted) with any user whose MUD client uses
         the zChat or MudMaster protocols.
      This command is the equivalent of typing ';chatgroup <text>' in any Chat
         task window in the <group>.

   User commands:
      chatg / chatgroup
